<li><a href="http://ati.iblp.org/ati/supportlink/kb/questions/88/How+can+I+meditate+on+Scripture%3F" class="external text" title="http://ati.iblp.org/ati/supportlink/kb/questions/88/How+can+I+meditate+on+Scripture%3F" rel="nofollow">How to Meditate on Scripture</a> by the Advanced Training Institute</li>
<li><a href="http://mattstone.blogs.com" class="external text" title="http://mattstone.blogs.com" rel="nofollow">Journeys In Between</a> A blog featuring evangelical approaches to meditation</li>
